customValues.infoDesc:
After wandering the halls for god knows how long, Boyfriend stumbles onto a new room. The room is filled with party decorations and such. After eyeing the room, he notices an oddly shaped figure holding a balloon in front of him. The figure turns to him. The figure was something known as a "Partygoer".




Based on the original Backrooms and tons of fanmade analog horror surrounding the concept.
